-- China Reaffirms Support for Europe Efforts to Solve Debt Crisis
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-07-10T09:17:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-10/china-reaffirms-support-for-europe-efforts-to-solve-debt-crisis.html
China  reaffirmed its support for the
European Union’s efforts to tackle its sovereign debt crisis as
the two sides concluded two days of talks as part of the EU-
China Strategic Dialogue today.  The two sides agreed to address their differences in a
constructive way and the EU affirmed its respect for China’s
territorial integrity, according to a joint statement released
today after the talks.  China and the EU also discussed their desire to develop
trade and investment links and will look at new ways to
collaborate, EU Foreign Policy Chief  Catherine Ashton  said in a
separate statement.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
Nicholas Wadhams in Beijing at 
